summary:
I made this mod for myself, as I thought that the final boss, Alduin, was too easy on max difficulty, as I could defeat him with nothing equipped what so ever, well this mod fixes that.
And I realized that others may, think the same thing, so I have uploaded it, for you all to use.
Compatible with all other mods.
descriptionHtml:
[size=5][u][i][b] Alduin Redone [/b][/i][/u][/size]

[size=1]I made this mod for myself, as I thought that the final boss, Alduin, was too easy on max difficulty, as I could defeat him with nothing equipped what so ever, well this mod fixes that.
And I realized that others may, think the same thing, so I have uploaded it, for you all to use.
Compatible with all other mods.[/size]

[size=1]What Does The Mod Do?[/size]
[size=1]It Makes The End Boss Alduin Stronger, Bigger Harder![/size]
author: Enoomnai
